{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-gui/pullrequests/62/comments/51438035.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-gui/pull-requests/62/_/diff#comment-51438035"}}, "parent": {"id": 51429857, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-gui/pullrequests/62/comments/51429857.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-gui/pull-requests/62/_/diff#comment-51429857"}}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 62, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-gui/pullrequests/62.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-gui/pull-requests/62"}}, "title": "Rendering plugins: Scene3D and Grid3D"}, "content": {"raw": "From 7eb4575 the camera and scene are being deleted. Then starting a new plugin will create a new scene:\n\n![scenedestroy.gif](data/bitbucket.org/repo/64K5zaR/images/1170803137-scenedestroy.gif)\n\nIf I finish the engine, the program crashes when I try to create a new plugin. I think that's because of what you said - the engine should be finished only when the program is about to be closed.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>From <a href=\"#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-gui/commits/7eb4575\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">7eb4575</a> the camera and scene are being deleted. Then starting a new plugin will create a new scene:</p>\n<p><img alt=\"scenedestroy.gif\" src=\"data/bitbucket.org/repo/64K5zaR/images/1170803137-scenedestroy.gif\" /></p>\n<p>If I finish the engine, the program crashes when I try to create a new plugin. I think that's because of what you said - the engine should be finished only when the program is about to be closed.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-12-07T21:06:23.638164+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Louise Poubel", "uuid": "{5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8/7d903d90-c5ea-4182-b7ef-0d467e9e1c74/128"}}, "nickname": "chapulina", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8"}, "updated_on": "2017-12-07T21:06:23.642668+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 51438035}